alerts.title: Flash Flood Watch for Collin, TX
alerts.description:
...FLASH FLOOD WATCH NOW IN EFFECT FOR ALL OF NORTH AND CENTRAL
TEXAS THROUGH LATE TONIGHT...
.THE GROUND REMAINS SATURATED FROM EXCESSIVE RAINFALL WHICH HAS
OCCURRED ACROSS MUCH OF THE REGION DURING THE LAST WEEK. LOCALLY
HEAVY RAIN WILL BE POSSIBLE THROUGH TONIGHT WHICH COULD LEAD TO
FLASH FLOODING.
...FLASH FLOOD WATCH NOW IN EFFECT THROUGH LATE TONIGHT...
